works.description: Two of my copyrighted photos are appearing on Google images without my authorization.   Both of the photos are of recording artist Roger Hodgson.   The photos were taken by me and are copyrighted to me.   They are on his official Facebook page with a disclaimer that they are copyrighted to me.   I would like for them to be removed from Google Images immediately.
